Kim Jong Il meets Jong Ju Yong and his son 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 1 (KCNA) -- The South Korean Hyundai Business Group sports team and working officers' group on a visit to Pyongyang visited the International Friendship Exhibition on Thursday.
   Exhibited there are hundreds of thousands of gifts presented to the great leaders President Kim Il Sung and Marshal Kim Jong Il by many party, state and government heads, figures from all walks of life and organizations around the world in profound reverence for them. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The visitors looked round the gifts with deep interest and commanded a bird's-eye view of scenery of the mountain from the balcony, listening to an immortal masterpiece poem "On Autumn Day In Mt. Myohyang" written by the president. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   They also visited the Mt. Myohyang History Museum.

